items.item: BGment Privacy Blackout Curtain Panel 7ft Tall, Navy Blue
description: Honestly, ugly as shit if you ask me. But I guess as long as it's dark, which is what these do, blackouts the room, who gives a shit how ugly the curtains are.

Listen I aint even gonna lie, check out the photo... This is nothing more than a fucking water hose, encased with an orange jacket of some sort to prevent tearing or puncture, perhaps melting or inceneration as well. Who Knows.

I honestly thought this was a fucking powerwasher because of the AC Plug extending from the jacket... But not quite, that just happens to exist, I don't pretend to understand why it was included in this hose, but it's there.

As for function, I assume it transmits water from a source out the far opposite end, as for the electricity aspect, don't ask me. I paid $40 because I thought it was a pressure washer, please at least take this off my hands at cost.
Yet another pendant light. This one is great because it's made out of bamboo, showing you support Communist China more-so than your very own nation.
But bamboo is a renewable resource, so I guess that's a plus. Just like human lives, but try not to burn through those like you do with the bamboo.
Light your kitchen table so your pale skin glows in the dark more and you can become depressed because your new lamp is making you look horrible.
